<% if (variant === 'text') { %>
  Hi,

  We received a request to reset your password for the SnowCMS instance hosted at <%= instance_url %>.

  For reference, this request was made from <%= ip_address %> using <%= browser %> on <%= os %>.

  If you requested this, you can reset your password here: <%= reset_link %>. This link expires after 15 minutes.

  If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.
<% } else { %>
    <mj-text>We received a request to reset your password for the SnowCMS instance hosted at <a href="<%= instance_url %>"><%= instance_url %></a>.</mj-text>

    <mj-text>For reference, this request was made from <%= ip_address %> using <%= browser %> on <%= os %>.</mj-text>

    <mj-text>If you requested this, you can reset your password here:</mj-text>

    <mj-button href="<%= reset_link %>">Reset password</mj-button>

    <mj-text>This link expires after 15 minutes.</mj-text>

    <mj-text>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.</mj-text>
<% } %>